fields.name: Lemon Cake
fields.description: Light, fluffy, and deliciously tangy, this Lemon Cake is the perfect dessert for any occasion. With two layers of moist lemon-flavored cake coated in a rich lime-flavored cream cheese frosting, thereâ€™s no shortage of bright lemon flavor in this dessert. You will absolutely fall in love with this tender cake after the first bite melts in your mouth.

fields.name: Carrot Cake
fields.description: Rich and moist spice cake, full of grated carrot, toasted nuts, and crushed pineapple, has great flavour, especially when covered with a tangy sweet Cream Cheese Frosting.

fields.name: Biscoff Cake
fields.description: A golden moist, fluffy vegan Biscoff sponge, layered with a smooth vegan Biscoff buttercream and a dreamy vegan Biscoff spread. Finished with crunchy Biscoff pieces and decorated with pretty flower petals, raspberry and strawberry crumb.

fields.name: Red Velvet Cake
fields.description: Strikingly beautiful and absolutely delicious; say hello to our Red Velvet cake, fit for any celebration. Baked to perfection with a rich chocolatey sponge, filled with oodles of light vanilla buttercream and topped off with stunning petals and crisp white pearls, this one's sure to impress.

fields.name: Chocolate Mousse Cake
fields.description: Indulgent and generous, this delicious fudgy cake is a slice of heaven with every bite! A rich chocolate bake with chocolate buttercream, layered in with smooth caramel and topped off with extra chocolate flakes!

fields.name: Chocolate Gateau
fields.description:
Our Chocolate Gateau is the perfect cake for any chocolate lover. Made with the most luxurious ingredients this cake has a taste of chocolate bliss in each bite.

Four layers of rich chocolate sponge filled with rich chocolate cream, white and dark chocolate pieces nestled inside. Coated in decadent chocolate buttercream and then dripped with a glossy chocolate ganache. Finished with chocolate cream rosettes and white and dark chocolate curls.

fields.name: Victoria Sponge Cake
fields.description: Named after Queen Victoria, this quintessentially British bake is simplicity at its best; sweet strawberry jam and pillowy soft cream, sandwiched between two light sponge cakes and a dusting of icing sugar and fruits. So put the kettle on and help yourself to a slice or two.

fields.description: With a huge range of flavours on offer, our mini cupcakes: muffins, cookies, tarts and macarons are perfect for those wanting a smaller bite, so check out our selection to satisfy your sweet cravings!
